Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

Buffalo Chicken 
Butter 65g
Hot water 0.9 cups
Flour 2 cups
Salt, big pinch
Handful of chives, finely chopped
1 chicken breast, shredded
½ cup hot sauce 
½ cup Butter, melted
1 tsp Garlic powder 
Blue cheese ranch, to serve
 
Sausage Marinara 
3 Pork sausages
½ Onion, diced
3 Garlic cloves, minced
1 tbsp tomato paste
400g tinned tomatoes
½ tsp Oregano 
½ tsp sugar
Splash of balsamic vinegar
Salt and pepper to taste
White bread, 8 slices
Pesto, to serve
 
Crunch-wrap 
500g Ground beef 
1 Onion, diced
2 tsp taco seasoning
Diced tomatoes, onion, and coriander 
Sour cream

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 sirloin steaks, sliced as thin as possible
* 	1 cup cream
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 cup beef stock
* 	2 cloves garlic, crushed
* 	1 small onion, finely chopped
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped
* 	lots of chips
* 	salt and pepper, to taste
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	3 tbsp butter
* 	1 tbsp black pepper, freshly ground
* 	1 cup parmesan, grated
